#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：原子性加法操作，在指定的内存位置执行原子加法\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Atomic addition operation, performs atomic addition at the specified memory location.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.atomic_add(\n"
"    pointer,\n"
"    val,\n"
"    mask=None,\n"
"    sem=None,\n"
"    scope=None,\n"
"    _semantic=None\n"
") -> pointer\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:8
msgid "可以作为tensor的成员函数调用，如`x.atomic_add(...)`，与`atomic_add(x, ...)`等效。"
msgstr "Can be called as a member function of a tensor, such as `x.atomic_add(...)`, which is equivalent to `atomic_add(x, ...)`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `pointer`        | `triton.PointerDType`          | 要操作的内存位置，执行 *pointer + val 计算后的结果写回到该内存                                                     |\n"
"| `val`       | `pointer.dtype.element_ty`    | 执行原子加法操作的值（右操作数）                                                        |\n"
"| `mask`     | `int1`或`tensor<int1>`，可选    | 指定数据范围，防止访问越界 |\n"
"| `sem` | `str`，可选 | 指定操作的内存语义<br>社区官方配置可接受的值为“acquire”、“release”、“acq_rel”（默认，代表“ACQUIRE_RELEASE”）和“relaxed”<br>我们只支持“acq_rel”：<br>- acquire：获取锁后，能够看到之前的释放操作（相当于一个“读取”操作，并且这个读取操作会阻塞，直到能够读取到“最新”的数据，也就是其他线程释放后的数据）<br>- release：在释放锁之前的所有操作，对后续获取锁的线程可见（相当于一个“写入”操作，并且这个写入操作会“同步”所有之前的写操作）                                             |\n"
"| `scope` | `str`，可选 | 观察原子操作同步效果的线程范围<br>可接受的值为“gpu”（默认）、“cta”（协作线程数组、线程块）或“sys”（代表“SYSTEM”） <br>我们只支持“gpu”                                            |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                               |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ---- | ----------- |\n"
"| `pointer` | `triton.PointerDType` | The memory location to operate on. The result of the *pointer + val computation is written back to this memory location. |\n"
"| `val` | `pointer.dtype.element_ty` | The value for the atomic addition operation (right operand). |\n"
"| `mask` | `int1` or `tensor<int1>`, optional | Specifies the data range to prevent out-of-bounds access. |\n"
"| `sem` | `str`, optional | Specifies the memory semantics of the operation.<br>Community official configuration accepts \"acquire\", \"release\", \"acq_rel\" (default, representing \"ACQUIRE_RELEASE\"), and \"relaxed\".<br>We only support \"acq_rel\":<br>- acquire: After acquiring the lock, previous release operations are visible (equivalent to a \"read\" operation that blocks until the \"latest\" data, i.e., data released by other threads, can be read).<br>- release: All operations before releasing the lock are visible to threads that subsequently acquire the lock (equivalent to a \"write\" operation that \"synchronizes\" all previous write operations). |\n"
"| `scope` | `str`, optional | The thread scope for observing the synchronization effect of the atomic operation.<br>Acceptable values are \"gpu\" (default), \"cta\" (cooperative thread array, thread block), or \"sys\" (representing \"SYSTEM\").<br>We only support \"gpu\". |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | Reserved parameter; external calls are not supported for now. |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Atomic_Ops/atomic_add.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`pointer`：tensor，执行操作之前的旧值\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`pointer`: tensor, the old value before the operation is performed.\n"

